name: Logo Design
description:
Get a new logo design for you or your company to give it some 'pop' and visual appeal for clients.
   Logo Design Package includes:
   -Design process begins with 4 logo concept ideas. Revisions as needed made to chosen concept, up to 4 hours total time
   -Final artwork saved in standard industry printing/web formats and emailed to client
   
   *$200 for package is required to begin project
   
   Hourly Rate $50/hr. w/1 hr. minimum
   -Designed for those who already have a solid idea and simply need it created digitally or have a current logo needing to be re-created for printing/web purposes.

options.name: Email for price quote request on re-creation/editing to an existing logo.

name: Screen Printing
description:
Lets dapper in ingenious design and create a t-shirt design for you or your business. Great for marketing, identity, business, family reunions, special events or just plain fun.

Apparel pricing prior to print varies from brand to brand and materials, and is based on selected quantities and specific product made by client.

Prior to beginning printing process, quotes will be provided. Quotes are provided with knowledgeable up-front information and are estimated as closely as possible. We reserve the right to apply charges to final bill for any variance from quote if necessary.

name: Graphic Design
description:
Our Graphic Design/Printing Service includes such items as: Wedding Invitations & Thank You Cards, Business Cards, Decals, Promotional Products and Marketing Material.
   
   Hourly Work is billed at $50/hr. with a 30 minute ($25)
minimum charge. Up-front estimates are based on initial client
needs and do not necessarily include revisions or additional
design work the client may ask for during or after the design process.

   To start the design process a deposit (half of quote) will be
required based upon up-front time estimates. Final design files
will be turned over to the client upon receipt of final balance
due. Design files will be emailed to client in standard industry
formats.

options.name: Email for price quote request on graphic design/printing materials.

name: Wedding Invitations
description:
HoBsoNVille will design and put together the right layout for your special wedding invitation.

   Wedding Invitation Package includes:
- Concept ideas from beginning to end on invitation, (any photos desired to be used on invitation must be provided by client prior to beginning the design process)
- Envelopes
- Gift registration information card
- One other separate/special invite, (i.e. ceremony or reception only).

name: Thank You Cards
description:
Thank You cards package includes:
- Concept ideas from beginning to end, (any photos desired to be used on invitation must be provided by client prior to beginning the design process)
- Envelopes
